{
  "title": "Cool Crunchy Kenyan Vegetable Skewers",
  "description": "A sour and shattering weeknight Kenyan dish featuring fajita seasoning, this Jain-friendly recipe is perfect for a quick dinner. It uses an ice-bath-shock to preserve the crunch of the vegetables.",
